<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: alpha genome excavator -->
  <GR_AlphaGenomeExcavator.label>阿尔法基因抽取器</GR_AlphaGenomeExcavator.label>
  <!-- EN: A simplified genome extraction device designed to be usable by even the most simple-minded goon, as such it resembles a caulking gun that works in reverse. The best genetic material can be found in the brain and the automated, single-use design instantly compresses this material into a usable genome.\n\nThe desired subject needs to be docile and trusting of the user who intends on scooping out their brain in a process that is not-quite instantaneous. It is recommended to anesthetize the creature as any sudden movement on their part will interrupt the whole process. Alternatively, it will also work on a dead body...\n\n<color=#E5E54C>Gameplay effect:</color> This excavator can be used to acquire the following genomes: -->
  <GR_AlphaGenomeExcavator.description>整体构造经过简化处理的一次性基因抽取工具。它的使用方式很像反过来工作的灌缝喷枪，即便是未开化的猴子也能轻松学会。生物的大脑里蕴含着最优质的基因，而这种工具的自动化设计能够立即将它们浓缩成可用的基因物质。\n\n你只能对已驯服的动物和尸体使用基因抽取器。由于动物的突然移动会打断抽取过程，先将它们麻醉或许是个不错的选择。\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C>游戏效果：&lt;/color>这种工具能够抽取的基因物质种类：</GR_AlphaGenomeExcavator.description>
  <!-- EN: Use genome excavator -->
  <GR_AlphaGenomeExcavator.comps.CompUsable.useLabel>使用基因抽取器</GR_AlphaGenomeExcavator.comps.CompUsable.useLabel>
  
</LanguageData>